    end

    %% Data Flow Connections
    Gmail -->|Webhook| N8N
    N8N -->|Route & Analyze| Honcho
    Honcho -->|Query| Deriver
    Deriver -->|Inference| Qwen3
    Qwen3 -->|Vector Search| Embedding

    N8N -->|API Call| RAExperts
    RAExperts -->|Analysis Result| Honcho

    N8N -->|Create/Update| OpenProject
    OpenProject -->|Status Query| N8N

    Honcho -->|Activity Log| VirtualOffice
    OpenProject -->|WP Changes| Honcho

    InfraAgents -->|Monitor/Report| Voting
    Voting -->|Signal| N8N
    N8N -->|Bridge| BusinessWorkspace

    BusinessWorkspace -->|Status Update| Honcho

    %% Network Connections
    T3610 ---|LAN 2.5G| GX10
    T3610 ---|LAN 2.5G| RPi
    GX10 ---|LAN 2.5G| RPi

